snippet.title: Mangli Renuka Yellamma | Bonalu Song 2025 | Full Song | Suresh Bobbili | Indravathi | Nakka Srikanth
snippet.description:
🎶 MANGLI RENUKA YELLAMMA | BONALU SONG 2025 🎉
Celebrate the divine power of Renuka Yellamma with this energetic Bonalu 2025 anthem! Sung by the sensational Mangli and composed by the dynamic Suresh Bobbili, this song is a tribute to Telangana’s rich folk culture and the fierce goddess worshipped across the region.

Feel the spiritual energy rise as beats, devotion, and traditional Telangana folk vibes come alive in this electrifying song.


#mangli  #manglisongs #bonalusong2025  #manglibonalusongs #telanganabonalu #bonalunewsongs #nakkasrikanth #oggukatha #baindlakatha #renukayellammasongs


Director - Damu Reddy 
Singers : Mangli, Nakka Srikanth Yadav & Indravathi Chauhan 
Music : Suresh Bobbili
Cherographey :  Shekar Virus 
Source : Oggu Katha & Bindla  Katha 
Sekarana : Nakka Srikanth Yadav
DOP - Tirupathi 
Editing: Nikhil Goud 
DI :  Mayasabha Studios 
Colorist : Anvesh
Stylist : Rishi Choudary 
Camera Assnts : Paramesh & Pencil Balu 
Publicity Designs : Rana 
Execution - Shiva Chauhan 
Manager : Megharaj 
Producer - Balu Nayak 

Makeup & Hair Done by swathis_makeup_academy  
Costume Disigner by : beauty meets  Fashion by Jeevana

*Special Thanks*
Jenwada Venkanna, Kamli Patel (DOP) & Dev Rathod

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle | MAIN TRAILER
snippet.description:
Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle is only in Movie Theatres September 12 ⚔️ https://demonslayer-movie.com

Tanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon.

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.

The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

snippet.description:
Presenting 'Chikitu' – The Official Music Video From Superstar Rajinikanth's #COOLIE
Directed By Lokesh Kanagaraj & Music By Anirudh.

Listen to the "Chikitu" on your favourite Streaming Platforms: https://orcd.co/chikitusong

#ChikituMusicVideo #Coolie #SuperstarRajinikanth #SunPictures #LokeshKanagaraj #Anirudh #cooliefirstsingle #cooliesong #cooliemovie #cooliemusicvideo #cooliedisco #cooliesongvideo
-------------------------------------------------
Song Title : Chikitu 
Album / Movie : Coolie
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Arivu
Vocals - T Rajhendherr, Anirudh Ravichander, Arivu
Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Rhythm Produced by Karthik Vamsi
Shehnai - Balesh
Acoustic Guitar - Keba Jeremiah
Keyboards, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya
Session Assistant - Shivakiran S

Recorded at:
Albuquerque Records, Chennai. Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S 
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Rupendar Venkatesh at Mix Magic
Music Coordinator - Velavan B
-------------------------------------------------
Music Video Credits:

Starring : T Rajhendherr, Anirudh Ravichander, Sandy, Arivu
Director Of Photography : Leon Britto
Editing : Philomin Raj
Production Designer : Sathees Kumar
Choreographer : Sandy
Costume Designer : Praveen Raja
Makeup : Sasikumar Paramasivam
Pro : Riyaz K Ahmed
Sound Mixing : Kannan Ganpat
Colorist : Ranga (Prasad)
Stills : V Sittrarasu
Publicity Designer: Gopi Prasannaa
Vfx Supervisor : Ajay
Associate Cinematographer : Yuva Karthick
Assistant Cinematographers : Neil Adams, Venkatesh, S.Rohith Kumar
Associate Editor : Mithun Arumugam
Assistant Editor : Tamilselvan Sakthivel, Alagar Naveen
Art Associate Director : G.Durairaj
Art Assistant : U.Vinothkumar , M.Deenathayal
Graphic Designer: Ss.Naresh Kumar
Associate Stylist: Naushad Ahmed
Assistant Stylist: Mahalekshmi K
1st Focus Puller : A. Murugan
Lights : Light N Light
Gaffer : R. Siva Shanmugam
Camera : Suresh
Sound & Nagara : PalPandi
Photoflood : Murali - KCL Lights
Gimbal : Selvam
Jimmy Jib : Seenu And Team
Direction Team : Santhosh Krishnan, Immanuel Prakash, Magesh Balasubramaniam, Rohith Surya, Nithyanandan Rajasekar, Ganesh Damodharan, Gowtham Neduncheziyan, Vivek Elango, Santhosh Kumar Namachivayam, Nebutt Najdorf, Praveen Gandhi,
Kt Sidhaarth, Vijay S Veeramani, Lohi Charan, Suriya Kumaran, Pragadeesh Alagirisamy.
Subtitles - Rekhs
-------------------------------------------------
Track Lyrics::

Ey Navurraa dey
Sound ah Yaetthu..
Deva Vaaraandey..

Ey Kaelraa dey
Kaelvi kaettu 
Usura vaangadhey..

Enga vena Kaettukko
Ella oorum paathuko
Thambi konjam thallikko
Coolie Varaan solliko..

Edhukku Paechu
Ozhunga Ukkaaru
Enakku Boss ey Kidayaadhu

Enemy dhosthu
Evanaa irundhaalum
Moraikkalaama 
Sari dhaan mudichudalaama..

Vambukku Neeya Izhukkaadha
Enkitta modhi ezhakkaadha
Pollaadha Venga 
Un moonji Veenga..

Na Potta Rule ah odaikkadha..
Ne mattum kaila kedaikkaadha..
Oppaari song ah..
Vechaachu Vaanga..

Enga vena Kaettukko
Ella oorum paathuko
Thambi konjam thallikko
Coolie Varaan solliko..!
-------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Jagannath Rath Yatra 2025 LIVE | Rath Yatra 2025 Live From Puri Jagannath Dham | Puri Festival
snippet.description:
Discover the vibrant and spiritual celebration of the Car Festival, also known as Rath Yatra, held in Puri, Odisha. Join us as we explore the grand procession of Lord Jagannath, Lord Balabhadra, and Goddess Subhadra as they journey from the Jagannath Temple to the Gundicha Temple in majestic chariots. Do like, share and subscribe.

#RathYatra #Puri #LordJagannath #Festival #RathYatra #JagannathRathYatra #PuriFestival #LordJagannath #JagannathPuri #Balabhadra #Subhadra #CarFestival #IndianFestivals #OdishaCulture #spiritualjourney 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DDNational
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DoordarshanNational
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ddnational
Follow us on Whatsapp Channel: https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029VaEWwQ27NoaADz9bGr0S

The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Puri Jagannath Ratha Yatra Episode 02 MCM
🌟 Welcome to Episode 02 of the Puri Yatra Special! 🌟
Join Middle Class Madhu and his hilarious family as they dive into the grandeur of Jagannath Rath Yatra in Puri! 🚩

This episode brings laughter, emotion, and a colorful cultural celebration like never before! Watch how Madhu’s parents, friends, and our beloved 1A Master team up to pull the chariot of Lord Jagannath, blending tradition with full-on FilmyMoji style comedy! 😂💥

From crowded rooftops to catchy dialogues, this is a visual feast filled with middle-class nostalgia, unity, and devotion.

📍 Don’t miss the fun!

snippet.description:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

In this mad fun episode of Samodu Vilayadu, your favourite OG trio — VJ Siddhu, Harshath Khan, and Adirchi Arun — enter the game zone, and things go from wild to wilder!

Episode 4436: Popatlal's Plan To Meet Chakori
------------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal is all set to propose to Chakori on the last day of the trip—but will fate allow their paths to cross?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the full episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: ENG W Vs IND W | 1st T20I | Cricket Highlights | India Women’s Tour Of England | 28th June 2025
snippet.description:
In the 1st of 5 T20Is, England women took on India women. England women won the toss and elected to field first. Thanks to an awesome ton by Smriti Mandhana 112 runs of 62 balls, India able to set the target of 210 runs. England women did not manage to hold on to the start and the whole team fell at the score of 113 runs. Thus India women won the 1st T20I by 97 runs.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Kannappa is one of the most highly anticipated Telugu films, starring Vishnu Manchu in a powerful role, with Rebel Star Prabhas in a special appearance. This mythological action-drama promises stunning visuals, gripping storytelling, and grand performances. Fans across the USA are eagerly awaiting its release, expecting a cinematic masterpiece that blends devotion and drama seamlessly.  

Kannappa is set to redefine mythological storytelling in Telugu cinema with its breathtaking visuals, intense performances, and a gripping narrative. Vishnu Manchu’s dedication to the titular role, along with Prabhas’s special cameo, adds immense star power to this grand spectacle. Early reviews from the USA suggest that the film delivers a perfect mix of devotion, action, and emotion, making it a must-watch for fans of Indian cinema.  

Director Mukesh Kumar Singh’s vision, combined with stellar music and VFX, elevates the film to an epic scale. Whether you're a fan of mythological dramas or high-octane action, Kannappa promises to be a memorable experience.

📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: Gujarati 👇

હો વરહાળુ  વાયરા વાયા યાદો ના વાદળ છાયા... (૨)
વરહાલુ વાયરા વાયા રે યાદો ના વડાલ છાયા
વરહાળુ વાયરા વાયા રે હે એ એ યાદો ના વાદળ છાયા
હો તમે મને યાદ આયા રે હે એ એ આંખે મારી આંશુ આયા રે
હો યાદ આઈ એ તારીખ જ્યારે છૂટા પડયાતા
ઉભો છુ એ જગ્યા એ છેલીવાર જયા મળ્યાતા
હો વરહાદ પાડવા માંડ્યો રે હે એ એ એ
તને યાદ કરી  રડયો રે... (૨)

હો ચમકે છે વિજળી ને કાળા ભમ્મર વાદળ
વરહાદ ની હારે હારે પલળે મારા પાપણ
હો ભુલી ગઈ છોના છોના મળતા ગોમ ના પાદર
નથી મળતી તુ નથી મળતા તારા વાવળ
હો રહી જયો હુ તારા પ્રેમ નો તરસ્યો
મન મુકી ને વરહાદ આજે બહુ વરર્સ્યો
રોમ કેવા લેખ લખ્યા રે હે એ એ એ..(૨)
પ્રેમ હોવા છતા ના મળ્યા રે
હો મારો હાચો પ્રેમ હોવા છતા ના મળ્યા રે....

હો ગયા રે વરહ જેમ પલડવુ તારી સાથે
આવી જાને એનો એ પ્રેમ છે તારી માટે
હો તારા નોમ વાળુ ટેટૂ દોરેલુ મારા હાથે
મળે જો તુતો રોવુ છે ભરીને બાથે
હો શુ દોસ આપુ તને દોસ તકદીરના 
નઇ લખી હોય તને મારી લકીરમાં
હો યાદો માં જીંદગી જાશે રે હે એ એ એ...(૨)
હો ઓ ઓ ઓ કયા ભવે ભેટો થાશે રે ...(3)

હો વરહાળુ  વાયરા વાયા યાદો ના વાદળ છાયા... (૨)
વરહાલુ વાયરા વાયા રે યાદો ના વડાલ છાયા
વરહાળુ વાયરા વાયા રે હે એ એ યાદો ના વાદળ છાયા
હો તમે મને યાદ આયા રે હે એ એ આંખે મારી આંશુ આયા રે
હો યાદ આઈ એ તારીખ જ્યારે છૂટા પડયાતા
ઉભો છુ એ જગ્યા એ છેલીવાર જયા મળ્યાતા
હો વરહાદ પાડવા માંડ્યો રે હે એ એ એ
તને યાદ કરી  રડયો રે... (૨)

હો ચમકે છે વિજળી ને કાળા ભમ્મર વાદળ
વરહાદ ની હારે હારે પલળે મારા પાપણ
હો ભુલી ગઈ છોના છોના મળતા ગોમ ના પાદર
નથી મળતી તુ નથી મળતા તારા વાવળ
હો રહી જયો હુ તારા પ્રેમ નો તરસ્યો
મન મુકી ને વરહાદ આજે બહુ વરર્સ્યો
રોમ કેવા લેખ લખ્યા રે હે એ એ એ..(૨)
પ્રેમ હોવા છતા ના મળ્યા રે
હો મારો હાચો પ્રેમ હોવા છતા ના મળ્યા રે....

હો ગયા રે વરહ જેમ પલડવુ તારી સાથે
આવી જાને એનો એ પ્રેમ છે તારી માટે
હો તારા નોમ વાળુ ટેટૂ દોરેલુ મારા હાથે
મળે જો તુતો રોવુ છે ભરીને બાથે
હો શુ દોસ આપુ તને દોસ તકદીરના 
નઇ લખી હોય તને મારી લકીરમાં
હો યાદો માં જીંદગી જાશે રે હે એ એ એ...(૨)
હો ઓ ઓ ઓ કયા ભવે ભેટો થાશે રે ...(3)

------------------------------------------------------------
After a terrifying night spent with Chakori, Bhide tries to warn the others but they laugh it off, blaming it on too much party sharty. Will Chakori return to prove him right?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

ko.title: 스므리티 만다나 센추리! | 하이라이트 - 잉글랜드 대 인도 | 2025년 제1회 여자 바이탈리티 IT20
ko.description:
ecb.co.uk에서 We Are England Cricket Supporters에 무료로 가입하고 티켓 우선 구매 등 다양한 혜택을 누리세요!

노팅엄 트렌트 브리지에서 열린 제1회 여자 바이탈리티 IT20 잉글랜드와 웨스트인디스의 경기 하이라이트를 시청하세요.

snippet.title: #Video | नथुनिया 2 | Nathuniya 2 | Official Music Video | Khesari Lal Yadav ft. Daisy Shah |New Song
snippet.description:
"नथुनिया" के धमाल के बाद, अब "नथुनिया 2" ले के आ गइल बा बवाल!
ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और बॉलीवुड सुपरस्टार डेज़ी शाह के धमाकेदार जोड़ी अब भोजपुरिया अंदाज़ में कर रही बा आगाज़!
"नथुनिया 2" – अब हो चुकल बा रिलीज़! 
देखीं, झूमीं और शेयर करीं — सिर्फ़ @SaregamaHumBhojpuri  पर!

After the superhit "Nathuniya", the storm continues with "Nathuniya 2"!
Get ready for the explosive bhojpuri-style duo of trending star Khesari Lal Yadav and bollywood star Daisy Shah — setting the screen on fire!
"Nathuniya 2" – OUT NOW!
Watch it, vibe to it & share it — only on @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song – Nathuniya 2 
Singer – Khesari Lal Yadav
Featuring – Daisy Shah
Lyrics & Music – Krishna Bedardi 
Composer – KRK Yadav
Music Arranger – VS Chauhan
Director - Sumit Kumar & Rohit Shetty
Choreographer - Rohit Shetty 
DOP - Jason Nambardar
Editor - Nitin FCP
Asst. Director - Pawan Pandey
Asst. Editor - Narendra Jaiswal
2nd Asst. Editor - Siddharth Tiwari
Post Production - Arts For Production 
Colorist - Tapasvi Asija

तोहरा पसंदीदा गाना उपलब्ध बानी सब OTT प्लैट्फ़ॉर्म पर !

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/2VtwXVYAd0jmj9HMCD7XKq
YouTube Music: https://music.youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_n4sDKpi-TSvqr1lU0eyDYvzpmp-yykzt0
Apple Music: https://itunes.apple.com/album/id/1821859252
JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/nathuniya-2/Z3XFA5Nolw4_
Gaana: https://gaana.com/album/nathuniya-2-bhojpuri-2025
Amazon Music: https://music.amazon.in/albums/B0FDR2DGWW

Lyrics:-

हो अपना अखियां में काजरा लगाके,
रखनी जुड़ा में साड़ी अटकाके,,
आ हमार पावडर क्रीम लागे हो जाई डिम बाटे एकही जगहिया खाली,,
हो सईया बिन नथुनिया के डाली,,

त चोली चिल्लाता ये राजा हो जल्दी आ जा हो,
कमर से साड़ी सरक जाता सीरिया जा हो,,
त करी अईसन सिंगार के 
बिन भतार के,
मन नाही करे रही झार के बिन भतार के,,
त कहे बिंदिया बलम तू सतावल कर कम लाल भईल बा घुसा से ओठलाली हो सईया बिन,,,

चूड़ी के शोर सखि भावे ना केहू बजावे ना,
सुना संगीत बा जवानी के केहू गावे ना,,
अब त लागे की कटी ना सर्दी ये बेदर्दी,
इ जवानी खेसारी के नामे मन करे करदी,,
रहिते घरे बलम होईत गाना गरम 
ओ में कबो कबो होईत कऊवाली ,, हो सइया बिन,,

snippet.title: Inside a Village with No Doors, No Locks & No Theft!  (SHOCKING 😲)
snippet.description:
This is one of the most unique villages in india! This is shani shingnapur village

Could you imagine living in a house without a door? I couldn't either, until I set foot in Shani Shingnapur! This legendary village in India is famous for its unique custom: homes are built without any doors, relying solely on the divine protection of Lord Shani. But my curious mind had questions: How do people live like this? What about security? And are the tales of zero theft truly real?

In this video, I take you with me as I explore every corner of Shani Shani Shingnapur. I spoke to residents, witnessed daily life, and dug into the local lore surrounding the "no theft" phenomenon. Get ready for a fascinating look into a community built on faith and trust. This was truly an eye-opening experience!

snippet.title: Bala Speech Parandhu Po, Vetrimaaran Speech Parandhu Po | Parandhu Po Audio Launch
snippet.description:
Bala Speech Parandhu Po, Vetrimaaran Speech Parandhu Po | Parandhu Po Audio Launch

Bala Speech Parandhu Po audio launch.
Vetrimaaran speech Parandhu Po movie trailer launch.
Bala Vetrimaaran speech in Parandhu Po movie trailer launch. 

Presenting Director Bala, Director Vetrimaaran speech Parandhu Po movie. Parandhu Po movie audio and trailer launch happened in chennai today.

Paranthu Po is an 2025 Indian Tamil-language road musical comedy film written, directed and co-produced by Ram under his banner Seven Seas and Seven Hills Productions along with Disney+ Hotstar. The film stars Shiva and Mithul Ryan in the lead roles alongside Grace Antony, Anjali, Vijay Yesudas, Aju Varghese and others in important roles. The music and background score was composed by Santhosh Dhayanidhi and Yuvan Shankar Raja, while the cinematography and editing were handled by N. K. Ekambaram and Mathi V. S. respectively.

Parandhu Po is scheduled to release in theatres on 4 July 2025.

snippet.title: PASTA | Prawn Masala Pasta Recipe Cooking in Village | Spirali Pasta Recipe | Seafood Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cooked a spirali pasta recipe using fresh prawns and colorful, healthy vegetables. We first half-cooked the pasta, then added it to a hot, big pan along with the prawns. We also added hand-ground masala for traditional taste and healthy, colorful vegetables to make this pasta both nutritious and tasty.

Finally, we enjoyed the dish in the evening at our farm. The taste was spicy and delicious!

it.title: PASTA | Ricetta della pasta con gamberi e masala | Cucinare nel villaggio | Ricetta della pasta a...
it.description:
Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato una pasta a spirale con gamberi freschi e verdure colorate e salutari. Abbiamo prima cotto la pasta a metà cottura, poi l'abbiamo messa in una padella grande e calda insieme ai gamberi. Abbiamo anche aggiunto masala macinato a mano per un sapore tradizionale e verdure sane e colorate per rendere questa pasta nutriente e gustosa.

Infine, abbiamo gustato il piatto la sera nella nostra fattoria. Il sapore era piccante e delizioso!

ja.title: パスタ | エビマサラパスタのレシピ 村で調理 | スパイラリパスタのレシピ | シーフードのレシピ
ja.description:
今日は村で、新鮮なエビと色とりどりのヘルシー野菜を使ったスパイラルパスタを作りました。パスタを半分ほど茹でてから、熱した大きなフライパンにエビと一緒に入れました。伝統的な味にするために、手挽きのマサラとヘルシーで色とりどりの野菜を加え、栄養価が高く、おいしいパスタに仕上げました。

最後に、農場で夕食を楽しみました。スパイシーでとても美味しかったです！

id.title: PASTA | Resep Pasta Masala Udang Masak di Desa | Resep Pasta Spirali | Resep Makanan Laut
id.description:
Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak resep pasta spirali menggunakan udang segar dan sayuran berwarna-warni yang menyehatkan. Pertama-tama kami memasak pasta setengah matang, lalu memasukkannya ke dalam wajan besar yang panas bersama udang. Kami juga menambahkan masala yang digiling dengan tangan untuk cita rasa tradisional dan sayuran berwarna-warni yang menyehatkan agar pasta ini bergizi dan lezat.

Akhirnya, kami menikmati hidangan ini di malam hari di pertanian kami. Rasanya pedas dan lezat!

es-US.title: PASTA | Receta de pasta masala con langostinos | Receta de pasta espiral | Receta de mariscos
es-US.description:
Hoy en nuestro pueblo, cocinamos una receta de pasta espiral con gambas frescas y verduras coloridas y saludables. Primero, cocinamos la pasta a medias y luego la pusimos en una sartén grande y caliente junto con las gambas. También añadimos masala molida a mano para darle un sabor tradicional y verduras coloridas y saludables, lo que hizo que esta pasta fuera nutritiva y sabrosa.

Por último, disfrutamos del plato por la noche en nuestra granja. ¡El sabor era picante y delicioso!

fr-FR.title: PÂTES | Recette de pâtes aux crevettes masala | Recette de pâtes spirales | Recette de fruits de mer
fr-FR.description:
Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons cuisiné des pâtes spirali avec des crevettes fraîches et des légumes sains et colorés. Nous avons d'abord mi-cuit les pâtes, puis les avons placées dans une grande poêle chaude avec les crevettes. Nous avons également ajouté du masala moulu à la main pour un goût traditionnel et des légumes sains et colorés pour des pâtes à la fois nutritives et savoureuses.

Nous avons finalement dégusté ce plat le soir à la ferme. C'était épicé et délicieux !

hi.title: पास्ता | झींगा मसाला पास्ता रेसिपी गांव में खाना बनाना | स्पाइरली पास्ता रेसिपी | समुद्री भोजन रे...
hi.description:
आज हमारे गांव में, हमने ताज़े झींगे और रंग-बिरंगी, सेहतमंद सब्ज़ियों का इस्तेमाल करके स्पाइरली पास्ता रेसिपी बनाई। हमने पहले पास्ता को आधा पकाया, फिर उसे झींगों के साथ एक गर्म, बड़े पैन में डाला। हमने पारंपरिक स्वाद के लिए हाथ से पिसा हुआ मसाला और सेहतमंद, रंग-बिरंगी सब्ज़ियाँ भी डालीं, ताकि यह पास्ता पौष्टिक और स्वादिष्ट दोनों बन सके।

आखिरकार, हमने शाम को अपने खेत में इस डिश का लुत्फ़ उठाया। इसका स्वाद मसालेदार और लज़ीज़ था!

de-DE.title: PASTA | Rezept für Garnelen-Masala-Pasta im Dorf kochen | Spiral-Pasta-Rezept | Meeresfrüchte-Rezept
de-DE.description:
Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein Rezept für Spiralnudeln mit frischen Garnelen und buntem, gesundem Gemüse gekocht. Wir haben die Nudeln zunächst halb gekocht und dann zusammen mit den Garnelen in eine große, heiße Pfanne gegeben. Für den traditionellen Geschmack haben wir handgemahlenes Masala und gesundes, buntes Gemüse hinzugefügt, um die Nudeln nahrhaft und lecker zu machen.

Abends haben wir das Gericht auf unserem Bauernhof genossen. Es schmeckte würzig und köstlich!

pt-BR.title: MASSAS | Receita de Massa Masala com Camarão | Cozinhando na Vila | Receita de Massa em Espiral |...
pt-BR.description:
Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos uma receita de macarrão espiral com camarões frescos e vegetais coloridos e saudáveis. Primeiro, cozinhamos o macarrão pela metade e depois o colocamos em uma panela grande e quente junto com os camarões. Também adicionamos masala moído à mão para um sabor tradicional e vegetais saudáveis ​​e coloridos para tornar este macarrão nutritivo e saboroso.

Por fim, apreciamos o prato à noite em nossa fazenda. O sabor era picante e delicioso!

pl.title: MAKARON | Przepis na makaron z krewetkami i masalą Gotowanie w wiosce | Przepis na makaron Spiral...
pl.description:
Dzisiaj w naszej wiosce ugotowaliśmy przepis na makaron spirali ze świeżymi krewetkami i kolorowymi, zdrowymi warzywami. Najpierw ugotowaliśmy makaron w połowie, a następnie dodaliśmy go do gorącej, dużej patelni razem z krewetkami. Dodaliśmy również mieloną ręcznie masalę dla tradycyjnego smaku i zdrowe, kolorowe warzywa, aby ten makaron był zarówno pożywny, jak i smaczny.

Na koniec, wieczorem delektowaliśmy się daniem na naszej farmie. Smak był pikantny i pyszny!

nl-NL.title: PASTA | Garnalen Masala Pasta Recept Koken in Dorp | Spirali Pasta Recept | Zeevruchten Recept
nl-NL.description:
Vandaag kookten we in ons dorp een recept voor spirali pasta met verse garnalen en kleurrijke, gezonde groenten. We kookten de pasta eerst half gaar en deden die vervolgens in een hete, grote pan, samen met de garnalen. We voegden er handgemalen masala aan toe voor de traditionele smaak en gezonde, kleurrijke groenten om de pasta zowel voedzaam als lekker te maken.

Tot slot hebben we 's avonds op onze boerderij van het gerecht genoten. Het was pittig en heerlijk!

ko.title: 파스타 | 마을에서 요리하는 새우 마살라 파스타 레시피 | 스파이럴리 파스타 레시피 | 해산물 레시피
ko.description:
오늘 저희 마을에서는 신선한 새우와 알록달록하고 건강에 좋은 채소를 넣어 스파이럴 파스타 레시피를 만들어 봤습니다. 파스타를 반쯤 익힌 후, 뜨겁고 큰 팬에 새우와 함께 넣었습니다. 전통적인 맛을 위해 손으로 간 마살라를, 영양가 있고 맛있는 채소를 더하기 위해 건강하고 알록달록한 채소를 넣었습니다.

마지막으로 저녁 농장에서 맛있게 먹었습니다. 매콤하면서도 정말 맛있었어요!

snippet.title: Ironheart Episodes 1-3 Breakdown - Mephisto Hints & Iron man Legacy | Explained in Hindi
snippet.description:

With connections to Tony Stark, Obadiah Stane, and possibly Mephisto, this MCU series explores what it takes to be a hero—without a billion-dollar bank account. In this breakdown, we explore the story, characters like Hood, Natalie, and Ezekiel Stane, the upgraded armor, comic parallels, and the chilling secrets behind that cursed cloak.

snippet.title: Adhure Supne | New Punjabi Series 2025 | JaggieTV
snippet.description:
Adhure Supne (Incomplete Dreams) A powerful story of struggle, dreams, and resilience.
In a world where every character is battling their own demons, Jaggi stands out — a young man with immense musical talent but no money to chase his dream. While he’s determined to record his songs and make his mark, his family pushes him to abandon his passion and take up a "real job."
Torn between expectations and ambition, Jaggi keeps sacrificing his dreams... until Seerat enters his life. Together, they face life's toughest challenges, stand tall against society, and fight to keep their dreams alive.
Will their incomplete dreams ever be fulfilled?Can passion survive in a world full of pressure?
Watch now to witness this emotional journey filled with inspiration, love, and the fire to never give up! 🔥

Producer: Jaggie Rajgarh
Executive Manager: Simardeep Singh
Production Manager: Dharminder Singh

Concept: Jaggie Rajgarh
